00:30:00.464 --> 00:30:04.284
DNA does. I think my colleague Ben

503
00:30:04.304 --> 00:30:06.154
Cravatt has a very good analogy of this.

504
00:30:06.644 --> 00:30:09.984
For years, people thought about microsatellite instability.

