566
00:33:49.400 --> 00:33:49.660
And

567
00:33:51.200 --> 00:33:54.400
what it does is it actually builds a graph out of

568
00:33:55.060 --> 00:33:58.640
these amplified regions, looking both at high copy numbers and

569
00:33:59.160 --> 00:34:02.880
the paired-end reads that connect distant high copy number

