575
00:34:17.781 --> 00:34:21.740
ecDNA. So it's relatively simple and crude, but it does work,

576
00:34:21.781 --> 00:34:25.680
and we also make other calls, those of breakage-fusion-bridge

577
00:34:25.740 --> 00:34:29.160
cycles, complex non-cyclic, and linear amplicons.

578
00:34:29.321 --> 00:34:33.000
And today, I'll go through the thinking process that we

