00:40:27.436 --> 00:40:31.186
Elizabeth Blackburn, both great scientists in the telomere

680
00:40:31.296 --> 00:40:34.865
field, suggested that there might be this healing process that

681
00:40:34.936 --> 00:40:37.916
allows these broken ends to reacquire telomeres.

682
00:40:37.925 --> 00:40:41.276
And it's not well understood, but now we have some data where we can

683
00:40:41.416 --> 00:40:45.076
start picking at this problem. And you can see in this one

684
00:40:45.136 --> 00:40:49.096
