00:40:52.856 --> 00:40:56.036
It's actually hijacking a portion of chromosome 15.

687
00:40:56.466 --> 00:41:00.356
You can see the increase in copy number and probably reacquires the telomere

688
00:41:00.366 --> 00:41:04.196
through this translocation. So hopefully with new data, we are

689
00:41:04.256 --> 00:41:06.916
able to get at the bottom line of these questions.

690
00:41:08.016 --> 00:41:11.376
So now when we have these two amplifications, a stable

