693
00:41:18.416 --> 00:41:22.116
And we have a lot of data. But I'll point to this example that Paul

694
00:41:22.156 --> 00:41:26.136
alluded to where when you look at extrachromosomal DNA and target

695
00:41:26.216 --> 00:41:26.416
them

696
00:41:27.636 --> 00:41:28.036
with this,

