711
00:42:18.516 --> 00:42:20.316
the extrachromosomal amplification.

712
00:42:21.776 --> 00:42:22.596
So

713
00:42:23.616 --> 00:42:26.606
what's left? So one thing is that even though we can

714
00:42:26.636 --> 00:42:29.056
